metadata.name: Genesis Wearechibizen Opening
metadata.description:
Wearechibizen are citizens of smol people. They love to seek adventure across the big big world. Along the way around, they found so many people with different experience and characters. 

They knew that they are smol but that does not stop them from growing with their big big heart. 

This animation is the beginning, the genesis of the Wearechibizen, Movement of smol people.

Collection : Wearechibizen (Foundation Edition)
Original Resolution : 1280 X 720
File size : 39,010,574 byte
Frame rate : 29.97 frames/second
Audio bit rate : 128kbps
